title: [BUG]A potential bug of NULL pointer dereference
body:
there is a potential bug of null pointer dereference.In **file sds.c,line 159**,zrealloc my fail to allocate memory,so it may incur null pointer dereference as following graph shows.
![Snipaste_2021-08-07_15-10-22](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/87304478/128591999-97accafb-cf7c-4269-b12b-5291511381ad.png)
Would you help to check whether this is a true bug? Thanks very much.
